              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Element Becerisi</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">2 </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Buz Hasarı </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">verir ve 1 </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Buzdan Tüy </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">oluşturur.</span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Buzdan Tüy</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Savaş Durumu</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">Karakterin verdiği </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Buz Hasarı </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">1 artar. (</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Buz tesirli </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">Girdap tepkimelerinden gelen Hasar dahil)</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Kullanım Hakkı: </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">3</span></p>",
