                "title": "Kutsal Kadının Hükmü"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Minyon</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Son Aşama: </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">1 </span><span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">Buz Hasarı </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">verir.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Kullanım Hakkı: </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">2 </span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">Bu Minyon savaş alanındayken rakip karakterler fazladan 1 </span><span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">Buz Hasarı </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">ve </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Fiziksel Hasar </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">alır.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/25/145542732/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_94924050028983956.png",
                "key": "Tılsım Ruhu",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/25/145542732/0729bd2530214665f6a30676963e3d6f_2384978626630344537.png",
                "title": "Tılsım Ruhu"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">Buz Etkisi uygular ve şu Element Tepkimelerini tetikleyebilir: <br>[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Buz </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">+ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Ateş</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">] </span><strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Erime: </span></strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">Bu seferki Hasar 2 artar.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Buz </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">+ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Elektrik</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">] </span><strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Süper İletim: </span></strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">Bu seferki Hasar 1 artar ve hedef dışındaki tüm rakip karakterlere 1 Delme Hasarı verir.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Buz </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">+ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Su</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">] </span><strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Donma: </span></strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">Bu seferki Hasar 1 artar ve hedef bu turda hamle yapamaz. (Hedef, Fiziksel Hasar ve Ateş Hasarı alınca kaldırılır, fazladan 2 Hasar alır.)</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/25/145542732/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_3003191382213568976.png",
